(44, 'todo', 'text/plain', '', '!rn addslashes remove slashes BS: edit basejs and watch the rn''s\n!weird checkbox/package display behavior.\n!edit places!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n!uploads\n!error pages (no movabl by that id, etc)\n!package details\n\ninterface details\n-switch node type options/configs per node\n-create a blank child node\n-order nodes\n-metadata\n\nmedia details\n-mimetype dropdown/create new\n-input editor per wfs-inputs\n-add new metadata fields-metadata\n-code editor per mimetype\n-upload/import file\n-manage file as media\n-cleanup-create media\n\nfunction details\n-code editor/tabs/color code by media css\n-input editor per wfs-inputs\n-add new metadata fields-metadata\n-cleanup-create function\n\nlaunchpad\n-center map\n-show hide packages\n\nplaces\n-create\n\n\n[] Build permissions into the overall system and API\n[] Caching places and setting modified dates so apache serves from the cache like it does with files\n[] Error handling / ability to create a place that you use for non-404 errors (maybe you go to the % place no matter what the error?)\n[] Line numbers in media rendering errors\n[] Limit access to $GLOBALS variables\n[] define/build globals our auto globals\n[] Put $FILES content into the globals array so it can be added to the database (adjust memorylimit after you know how big the files are).\n[] Global stuff\n[] PHP settings for security  how do other shared hosts do it?\n[] Add delete functionality to the Movabls API\n[] Development Environment');
